song_name: Zombie By The Cranberries By Andrew Jackson Jihad

version_description: Also, the placement of the Eb and Dm's might be a little off, but it copies the same pattern throughout the song. If you sing along with it you should be able to figure it out. When there are three Eb's in a row the second two are 8th notes, or you could play a single Eb but do an arpeggio instead of a chord. I'm playing via piano so just play what sounds right for you.
From the album Trouble in Shangra-la.
